    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/7ab231a5bda052e37f9fbe6d6a3855a3.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/f24f9c615a0fee7640810531b2272834.poster.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/f24f9c615a0fee7640810531b2272834.webm?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/f24f9c615a0fee7640810531b2272834.mp4?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of darkness and chaos. In Voidzone, society has been shattered by the rise of horrific anomalies and monstrous creatures, leaving humanity on the brink of extinction. As a designated cleaner for the remaining of human society, your mission is to venture and cleanse the dangerous hotspots of these anomalies also known as Voidzones. Once anomalies and a deadly infection now overrun thriving cities. Do you choose to follow your duty as a cleaner or change your fate and escape the city saving your own life? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/ebccd707459cbb6442805c85edc4c156.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/3c7c98b554015b190b9fbdb3997ed8e8.poster.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/3c7c98b554015b190b9fbdb3997ed8e8.webm?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/3c7c98b554015b190b9fbdb3997ed8e8.mp4?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Horror Experience:</strong> You are no fighter or hero. You are completely alone and can only run and hide. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person Adventure Horror:</strong> Immerse yourself in a gripping atmosphere full of tension and fear </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cleaner's Duty:</strong> Cleanse the anomalies present in the Voidzones and help restore society</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide and Sneak:</strong> Stealth-based gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Monsters:</strong> Every monster has a different playstyle making it a unique interaction between the player and the enemy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/d6287022e916e79a104f89463276f90f.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/01d1fa809259a8e772718eadbbd36dec.poster.avif?t=1734148953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/01d1fa809259a8e772718eadbbd36dec.webm?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123030/extras/01d1fa809259a8e772718eadbbd36dec.mp4?t=1734148953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
